Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a new encryption scheme to enhance the security of image transmission through untrusted channels. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with image encryption and compression. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is another possible category as the paper deals with image scrambling and color information. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possible category as the paper may involve information theoretic analysis of the proposed encryption scheme. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a less likely category, but it may be relevant as the paper evaluates the effectiveness of the proposed scheme for image transmission through social networking services.
